[
  {
    "chat_id": 2000001,
    "date": 1760486400,
    "from_id": 64578397655,
    "message_id": 1000000,
    "reply_to_message_id": 0,
    "text": "Mateo, looking for natural turquoise cabs for cuff work. Sleeping Beauty blue if you have it, plus some greener Sonora. What can you supply this autumn."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": 2000001,
    "date": 1760572800,
    "from_id": 61107864963,
    "message_id": 1000001,
    "reply_to_message_id": 0,
    "text": "I have both. Sonora green is steady, the blue comes and goes. Tell me the sizes and grade you want and I will quote a tray."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": 2000001,
    "date": 1760659200,
    "from_id": 64578397655,
    "message_id": 1000002,
    "reply_to_message_id": 0,
    "text": "Mostly 18 by 25 ovals and some freeform for bolo slides. Natural, no stabilised. Hard, tight matrix. A tray of forty to start."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": 2000001,
    "date": 1760745600,
    "from_id": 61107864963,
    "message_id": 1000003,
    "reply_to_message_id": 0,
    "text": "Forty natural cabs in that mix is around four hundred dollars. All hand cut, photos before I ship. Matrix is tight on this batch."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": 2000001,
    "date": 1760832000,
    "from_id": 64578397655,
    "message_id": 1000004,
    "reply_to_message_id": 0,
    "text": "Four hundred works if the blue holds its colour. Send the photos and I will pick the tray. Paying by transfer same day."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": 2000001,
    "date": 1760918400,
    "from_id": 61107864963,
    "message_id": 1000005,
    "reply_to_message_id": 0,
    "text": "Good. Photos tonight. The blue is real Sonora, it will not fade. I will hold the tray once you confirm."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": 2000002,
    "date": 1762300800,
    "from_id": 64578397655,
    "message_id": 1000006,
    "reply_to_message_id": 0,
    "text": "Lucia, do you carry coral and spiny oyster alongside the turquoise. I set a lot of red and orange next to silver and need a steady source."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": 2000002,
    "date": 1762387200,
    "from_id": 37145006549,
    "message_id": 1000007,
    "reply_to_message_id": 0,
    "text": "We do. Deep red coral branch and orange spiny oyster, cut to order. Coral is sold by weight, oyster by the piece. How much do you need."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": 2000002,
    "date": 1762473600,
    "from_id": 64578397655,
    "message_id": 1000008,
    "reply_to_message_id": 0,
    "text": "Maybe thirty grams of coral cabs and a dozen oyster ovals. The oyster is for a Sedona gallery that keeps asking. Need consistent orange."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": 2000002,
    "date": 1762560000,
    "from_id": 37145006549,
    "message_id": 1000009,
    "reply_to_message_id": 0,
    "text": "Thirty grams of coral is about two hundred and twenty. The oyster I can match for colour, a dozen ovals for ninety. Both natural."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": 2000002,
    "date": 1762646400,
    "from_id": 64578397655,
    "message_id": 1000010,
    "reply_to_message_id": 0,
    "text": "That is fair. Put the coral and oyster on the same shipment as Mateo's turquoise if you can. Saves on the freight."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": 2000002,
    "date": 1762732800,
    "from_id": 37145006549,
    "message_id": 1000011,
    "reply_to_message_id": 0,
    "text": "We can combine them. One box, one invoice. Mateo and I work out of the same shop, so it ships together from Hermosillo."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": 2000003,
    "date": 1764115200,
    "from_id": 64578397655,
    "message_id": 1000012,
    "reply_to_message_id": 0,
    "text": "Carlos, how do you handle the border crossing on the stone shipments. I want this declared properly, natural turquoise and coral for a studio."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": 2000003,
    "date": 1764201600,
    "from_id": 26625170722,
    "message_id": 1000013,
    "reply_to_message_id": 0,
    "text": "We declare every box at full value with the invoice inside. Natural stone, no restriction. It clears at Nogales and runs courier to Gallup."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": 2000003,
    "date": 1764288000,
    "from_id": 64578397655,
    "message_id": 1000014,
    "reply_to_message_id": 0,
    "text": "How long door to door once it leaves the shop. I have a gallery restock due and cannot have it stuck at customs."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": 2000003,
    "date": 1764374400,
    "from_id": 26625170722,
    "message_id": 1000015,
    "reply_to_message_id": 0,
    "text": "Five to seven days normally. I send the tracking when it crosses. If customs flags it they want the invoice, which is already inside."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": 2000003,
    "date": 1764460800,
    "from_id": 64578397655,
    "message_id": 1000016,
    "reply_to_message_id": 0,
    "text": "Understood. Insure it for the declared value. If it goes missing I need to cover the stone, not just the postage."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": 2000003,
    "date": 1764547200,
    "from_id": 26625170722,
    "message_id": 1000017,
    "reply_to_message_id": 0,
    "text": "Insured to full value, included. You will have the tracking number the day it ships. Nothing has gone missing on this route yet."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": 2000004,
    "date": 1766188800,
    "from_id": 2185195378,
    "message_id": 1000018,
    "reply_to_message_id": 0,
    "text": "Sam, can you do three more cuffs by month end. The turquoise ones sold out and people keep asking for the deep blue."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": 2000004,
    "date": 1766275200,
    "from_id": 64578397655,
    "message_id": 1000019,
    "reply_to_message_id": 0,
    "text": "Doable. I have a tray of Sonora coming from Mateo, natural blue. Three heavy cuffs, stone set, by the thirtieth. I will photograph them for you."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": 2000004,
    "date": 1766361600,
    "from_id": 2185195378,
    "message_id": 1000020,
    "reply_to_message_id": 0,
    "text": "Perfect. Price them the same as last time. The gallery takes its cut and the rest is yours on delivery."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": 2000005,
    "date": 1767916800,
    "from_id": 64578397655,
    "message_id": 1000021,
    "reply_to_message_id": 0,
    "text": "Stone order is placed with the Mexico supplier. Now I need silver. Annealing cuff blanks this week, want to set the new turquoise straight away."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": 2000005,
    "date": 1768003200,
    "from_id": 2023097178,
    "message_id": 1000022,
    "reply_to_message_id": 0,
    "text": "Sunwest sheet came in clean this batch. You complained about the old pin for a year, so I had them send heavier gauge. Order more solder."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": 2000005,
    "date": 1768089600,
    "from_id": 64578397655,
    "message_id": 1000023,
    "reply_to_message_id": 0,
    "text": "Already ordered solder and bezel wire. That holds me through the gallery restock if nothing burns up on the bench."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": 2000005,
    "date": 1768176000,
    "from_id": 2023097178,
    "message_id": 1000024,
    "reply_to_message_id": 0,
    "text": "Good. Set the best blue cab first while your eye is fresh. The matrix on those Sonora stones reads better in daylight."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": 2000006,
    "date": 1770508800,
    "from_id": 64578397655,
    "message_id": 1000025,
    "reply_to_message_id": 0,
    "text": "Thomas, the supplier sent photos of forty natural turquoise cabs. How do I judge grade from a picture before I pay four hundred dollars."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": 2000006,
    "date": 1770595200,
    "from_id": 3253260619,
    "message_id": 1000026,
    "reply_to_message_id": 0,
    "text": "Look at the matrix and the polish. Natural stone has a deep even shine, stabilised looks waxy. Ask if it is backed. Backed cabs are thinner than they look."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": 2000006,
    "date": 1770681600,
    "from_id": 64578397655,
    "message_id": 1000027,
    "reply_to_message_id": 0,
    "text": "He says natural, no stabilising, some backed for the thin ones. Blue Sonora and green. Price seems right against what Ray charges locally."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": 2000006,
    "date": 1770768000,
    "from_id": 3253260619,
    "message_id": 1000028,
    "reply_to_message_id": 0,
    "text": "Then it is a fair lot. Backed is fine for cuffs, it protects the stone. Buy the tray and set the hardest blue in the heavy silver."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": 2000006,
    "date": 1770854400,
    "from_id": 64578397655,
    "message_id": 1000029,
    "reply_to_message_id": 0,
    "text": "That is what I will do. Cheers Thomas. I will bring a finished cuff up to Santa Fe so you can see how the matrix sets."
